data.description: Welcome to your dream family home! This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem is a perfect blend of modern elegance and comfort. Updated wood laminate throughout and stainless steel appliances. Situated in a charming community, this house boasts a host of desirable features that make it a must-see. Enjoy your community pool, spa, and children's playground. With just a short commute to the ever-growing amenities of the San Tan Valley/Queen Creek area, you can get to San Tan Flats, Schnepf Farms, and countless other shopping opportunities. Come check out your new home!
